reviewText: Buy it it kicks love it, and the grandparents
My kids love watching baby Abuelita. It is very fun and entertaining to watch. It makes you want to get up and dance with them. Great for kids to start learning some spanish.

Great for little kids.  I gave this to my niece and she was very excited to watch this.  I got this after getting the doll (called abuelita rosa), which she also loved to carry around and bring with her everywhere.  This product does a much better job than Dora at explaining the language and trying to immerse them in the language.
I purchased this for my son because it has a lot of songs from my husband's childhood.  My son loves watching it.
